# Using a classic tokenizer
POST /myindex/_close

PUT /myindex/_settings
{
  "settings": {
    "analysis": {
      "tokenizer": {
        "classic": {
          "max_token_length": 5
        },
      },
      "analyzer": {
        "my_analyzer": {
          "tokenizer":  "classic"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

POST /myindex/_open

GET /_analyze?analyzer=my_analyzer&text=Let the wild rumpus start! (bit.ly/1wsCiKv)